Technology stack for Q10NIK:
1. DATABASE:
   FastDB       - github.com/gavioto/fastdb
2. GUI:
   - FLTK GUI
   - ncurses (text gui)
   
======= Column-oriented databases (openssource):
MariaDB                         - fast growing (mysql founders)
crate.io                        - make clusters of db
greenplum.org                   - massively scale oriented databse for big data
hypertable.com                  - entirely in c++
monetdb.org                     - column-store pioneer
voltdb                          - next-generation SQL RDBMS with ACID
eventql.io                      - dictributed column-oriented database in c++

======= key-value databases
aerospike.com                   - fastest NoSQL database (better than Redis)
scylladb
FastDB                          - c++ application layer database
                                  github.com/gavioto/fastdb
LMDB                            - fastest key-value db
